    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the Morrison CFD hemolysis model under CPB conditions is accepted at MRL 2. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed; all assessed factors met or exceeded their required credibility levels. The remaining six factors were appropriately scoped out or designated not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. The model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions with RH predictions within 13% of experimental measurements across all five operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device.",
